{"tid":216868,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4年代有咩 game 著重遊戲性多過畫質?","createTime":"2017-04-25T13:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T06:14:52.000Z","uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61582d692c58da277b85db0d42e81f23f3977742","tid":216868,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"首先解釋翻咩係遊戲性, 因為有好多人會將畫質同 fps 列入為影響遊戲性原素.<br />\n<br />\n遊戲性，或稱可玩性，是電子遊戲術語，體現遊戲的所有內在成分對玩家體驗的影響，而成份可以包括遊戲規則、遊戲與玩家的互動、遊戲的挑戰性及通關難度等，也就是「玩家能做什麼」。一般意義上，遊戲性高就是指玩家有各種各樣的事情可做。而遊戲的遊戲性是不會受遊戲的畫面美工、背景音樂及聲效的評價影響。(個人認為原創性都係重要原素之一)<br />\n<br />\n咩叫遊戲性強嘅 game? 以下有幾個列子:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m0.joe.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/09143544/metal-gear-solid-game.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm0.joe.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F09143544%2Fmetal-gear-solid-game.png&h=2d7ba810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.paopaoche.net/up/2015-7/2015714174217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.paopaoche.net%2Fup%2F2015-7%2F2015714174217.jpg&h=66c0f2ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/monsterhunter/images/5/51/Monster_Hunter_Coverart.png/revision/latest?cb=20080801100406\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fmonsterhunter%2Fimages%2F5%2F51%2FMonster_Hunter_Coverart.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20080801100406&h=72a88e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.amazon.com/images/P/B00005OVNP.09._SCLZZZZZZZ_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.amazon.com%2Fimages%2FP%2FB00005OVNP.09._SCLZZZZZZZ_.jpg&h=8839f0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.gamefaqs.net/box/3/8/8/40388_front.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.gamefaqs.net%2Fbox%2F3%2F8%2F8%2F40388_front.jpg&h=7f3245c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0514-1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2F0514-1a.jpg&h=14374b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.dwstatic.com/group1/M00/AE/D9/aed9b00d43fd735957a41f148281e7979249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.dwstatic.com%2Fgroup1%2FM00%2FAE%2FD9%2Faed9b00d43fd735957a41f148281e7979249.jpg&h=55597871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/618ZJ8YT5SL._AC_SX215_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F618ZJ8YT5SL._AC_SX215_.jpg&h=cffa891b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/75/CrazyTaxi_cover.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F7%2F75%2FCrazyTaxi_cover.png&h=9d8e37c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭先係 IGN 見到依隻 game, 令我諗翻起遊戲性依樣嘢. 唔知大家覺得佢嘅遊戲性又高唔高呢?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ign/videos/10154726713586633/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fign%2Fvideos%2F10154726713586633%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=4e68a3e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ign/videos/10154726713586633/</a>"},{"pid":"6430511ea2450c52246d00f8a0bbecf24ca97808","tid":216868,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"dark souls 3<br />\nBloodborne"},{"pid":"97cd774dfc981935ef109b023237177c97fc340b","tid":216868,"uid":85209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Persona5</span></span>"},{"pid":"66c6aa2c27574cacfee7f53e7a1d68e56cad0cf6","tid":216868,"uid":283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep